@startuml SDA_Pro_Component_Diagram
skinparam componentStyle uml2
title SDA-Pro — SOA Component and Event-Driven Architecture

actor "SOC Analyst" as Analyst
cloud "Mock External Security Sources" {
  [Splunk SIEM] as Splunk
  [Firewall Logs] as Firewall
}
cloud "Mock Threat Intel Providers" {
  [VirusTotal API] as VT
  [MISP API] as MISP
}

package "SOC Dashboard (MVC)" {
  [Controllers] as Controllers
  [Models] as Models
  [Views] as Views
}

package "SOA Service Layer" {
  [Alert Ingestion Service] as AIS
  [Enrichment & Correlation Service] as ECS
  [Incident Management Service] as IMS
  [Response Orchestration Service] as ROS
  [Threat Intel Service] as TIS
  [Notification Service] as NS
  [Audit Service] as AS
}

queue "In-Memory Event Bus\n(Observer Prototype)" as Bus
node "In-Memory Repositories" as Repo

Analyst --> Views : monitors/responds
Views --> Controllers : user actions
Controllers --> Models : data binding
Controllers --> IMS : incident queries
Controllers --> ROS : manual response

Splunk --> AIS : mock alert
Firewall --> AIS : mock alert
AIS --> ECS : CanonicalAlert
ECS --> IMS : create incident
ROS --> TIS : reputation check
ROS --> NS : dispatch notification
TIS --> VT : adapter call
TIS --> MISP : adapter call

AIS ..> Bus : AlertIngested
ECS ..> Bus : AlertEnriched
IMS ..> Bus : IncidentCreated\nIncidentStateChanged
ROS ..> Bus : ResponseActionExecuted
Bus ..> Views : DashboardUpdater
Bus ..> AS : AuditLogger
Bus ..> NS : NotificationDispatcher
Bus ..> Repo : MetricsCollector

AIS --> Repo : alert records
IMS --> Repo : incident records
AS --> Repo : audit trail
@enduml
